HTML-LESS-JavaScript Grunt Boilerplate
======================================

**How to install**
```
    npm install
    grunt
```


**Where put your files**
```
    .
    ├── .ftppass ← Servers password for automatic deploy
    ├── dist ← 'Compiled' files ready for browsers
    ├── Gruntfile.js
    ├── LICENSE
    ├── package.json
    ├── README
    └── src
        ├── css ← Your main.less
        ├── data.json ← Your app data
        ├── index.hbs
        ├── js ← Your main.js
        └── partials ← Your partials view
```
